%^BOLD%^-=%^RED%^Tyranny Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Clerics who choose the tyranny domain are typically fond of 
throwing their weight around and making others obey their 
whims.  The domain grants access to spells that affect the 
will of their foes as well as the ability of the foes to 
use certain magical abilities.

The tyranny domain contains the following spells:
Oppression (2nd), Fear (5th), Forbiddance (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     